{"questionId":"11850","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>A&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"2 \\times 2\">\n  <mn>2</mn>\n  <mo>×</mo>\n  <mn>2</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp;transition matrix for a Markov chain will have the form <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\mathbf{M}} = \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  a&amp;{1 - b} \\\\   {1 - a}&amp;b  \\end{array}} \\right){\\text{,}}\\,\\,0 < a < 1{\\text{,}}\\,\\,0 < b < 1\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi mathvariant=\"bold\">M</mi>\n    </mrow>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>a</mi>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>b</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>a</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>b</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n  <mo>&lt;</mo>\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mo>&lt;</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n  <mo>&lt;</mo>\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mo>&lt;</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n</math></span>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Find the steady state probability vector for&nbsp;<strong>M</strong>&nbsp;in terms of <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n</math></span> and <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"b\">\n  <mi>b</mi>\n</math></span>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  a&amp;{1 - b} \\\\   {1 - a}&amp;b  \\end{array}} \\right)\\,\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  p \\\\   {1 - p}  \\end{array}} \\right) = \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  p \\\\   {1 - p}  \\end{array}} \\right) \\Rightarrow ap + 1 - b - p + bp = p\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>a</mi>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>b</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>a</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>b</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>p</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>p</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>p</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>p</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mi>p</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mi>p</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mi>p</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>p</mi>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>M1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" \\Rightarrow 1 - b = \\left( {2 - a - b} \\right)p \\Rightarrow p = \\frac{{1 - b}}{{2 - a - b}}\">\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mi>b</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mi>p</mi>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>p</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mi>b</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mi>b</mi>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>&nbsp;<em><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; M1</strong></em></p>\n<p>So vector is&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {\\frac{{1 - b}}{{2 - a - b}}} \\\\   {\\frac{{1 - a}}{{2 - a - b}}}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mi>b</mi>\n                </mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mi>a</mi>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mi>b</mi>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mi>a</mi>\n                </mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mi>a</mi>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mi>b</mi>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;<em><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; A1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[5 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"11850","referenceCode":"EXM.1.AHL.TZ0.18b","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Find the steady state probability vector for M in terms of a and b .","paper":"1","level":"HL","questionNumber":"b","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 5]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 4—Statistics and probability","Topic 4—Statistics and probability","AHL 4.19—Transition matrices – Markov chains"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}